<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Child Account Deletion Requested</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #333; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px;">
    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-weight: 600;">Child account deletion requested</h2>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Hi {{parentName}},</p>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">We've received your request to delete <strong>{{childName}}</strong>'s account. The account has been deactivated and will be permanently deleted on <strong>{{gracePeriodEnd}}</strong>.</p>

    <div style="padding: 16px; background-color: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #92400e;"><strong>Note:</strong> After {{gracePeriodEnd}}, all data associated with this account will be permanently erased and cannot be recovered.</p>
    </div>

    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">To cancel this request, contact us at privacy@Examforge.com before that date.</p>
  </body>
</html>
